      "module_path": "tddd::catalogue_to_extended_crate_codec",
      "docs": "Stateless codec converting CatalogueDocument to ExtendedCrate (TypeGraph A). Modified in this track: (1) validate_supported_bound private method is removed and the codec accepts all syn-parseable bound strings without rejection (ADR D1 / IN-02; T002 done); (2) rustdoc impl-block and trait-declaration level generics are placed into the correct catalogue fields (ADR D2 / IN-09; T007 done); (3) CatalogueDocument.trait_impls top-level Vec is processed in a top-level loop in run(), resolving each trait_ref and for_type and encoding each entry into TypeGraph A with entry.action preserved (ADR 2026-05-20-0048 D1/D4 / IN-15 / IN-16; T013-T014 planned). The actual action-driven S-insertion (Add/Modify/Reference/Delete semantics) is performed by signal evaluator Phase 1 (T015). The public shape (unit_struct + encode via port) is unchanged.",
