      "module_path": "tddd::signal_evaluator_v2",
      "docs": "Stateless secondary adapter implementing SignalEvaluatorPort. Modified in this track by six changes: (1) strip_outlives_from_index removed and fingerprint generation updated for {lhs, rhs, operator} structure (ADR D1 / IN-03 / IN-04; T003 done); (2) symmetric comparison logic added for impl-block and trait-declaration generics (InherentImplDeclV2.impl_generics / TraitImplDeclV2.impl_generics / TraitEntry.generics vs rustdoc counterparts) (ADR D2 / IN-09; T007 done); (3) a_id_remap Pre-step added to Phase 1 builder (ADR D3 / IN-10; T008 done); (4) patch_impl_for_ids and patch_impl_trait_ids deleted from Phase 1 (ADR D3 / IN-11; T009 done); (5) C-side build_impl_identity_map for_is_external filter removed so cross-crate impls are included in c_impls symmetrically (ADR 2026-05-20-0048 D3 / IN-13; T012 done); (6) A-side orphan-impl detection path to be unified into CatalogueDocument.trait_impls top-level loop; all trait impls to be processed via single action-driven S-insertion path (ADR 2026-05-20-0048 D4 / IN-16; T015 planned). The public shape (unit_struct + evaluate via port) is unchanged.",
